==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Necked
<hw>Necked</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
(such) a neck; -- chiefly used in composition; <as>as,
stiff-<ex>necked</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>Cracked; -- said of a
treenail.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Neckerchief</ent>⟦br⟧
